{"an4.221:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.221 ","an4.221:0.2":"23. Duccaritavagga ","an4.221:0.3":"Duccaritasutta ","an4.221:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, vaciduccaritani. ","an4.221:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.221:1.3":"Musavado, pisuna vaca, pharusa vaca, samphappalapo—","an4.221:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari vaciduccaritani. ","an4.221:1.5":"Cattarimani, bhikkhave, vacisucaritani. ","an4.221:1.6":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.221:1.7":"Saccavaca, apisuna vaca, sanha vaca, mantavaca—","an4.221:1.8":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari vacisucaritani”ti. ","an4.221:1.9":"Pathamam. "}